{"Id":483,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-majian1","Author":"Ma Jian","Language":"Chinese(traditional)","Description":"Chinese(traditional)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"http://tanzil.net","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":41,"Text":"敬畏的人們，必定在樹蔭之下，清泉之濱，"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":42,"Text":"享受他們愛吃的水果，"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":43,"Text":"將對他們說：「你們曾經行善，故你們痛快地飲食吧！」"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":44,"Text":"我必定這樣報酬行善的人們。"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":45,"Text":"在那日，傷哉否認真理的人們。"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":46,"Text":"「你們暫時吃喝享受吧！你們確是犯罪的人。」"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":47,"Text":"在那日，傷哉否認真理的人們！"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":48,"Text":"有人對他們說：「你們當鞠躬。」他們不肯鞠躬。"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":49,"Text":"傷哉否認真理的人們！"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":50,"Text":"除《古蘭經》外，他們要信仰什麼文辭呢？"}]}